                    <span>This book is a great resource for helping to plan the deployment of XP.  I've been able to use many of the ideas and tips from the book to help redesign my deployment plan for my own company.  A great job was done by Jerry in writing and explaining the different ways to deploy XP.  Excellent Job, Excellent Book!!!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">a Clear and useful guide</div>
